# Accessibility Remediation Examples

### Image Alt
❌ `<img src="logo.png">`  
✅ `<img src="logo.png" alt="Auditvia logo">`

### Button Labels
❌ `<button></button>`  
✅ `<button aria-label="Submit form"></button>`

### Color Contrast
❌ `color: #999; background: #fff;`  
✅ `color: #333; background: #fff;` (contrast > 4.5:1)

### Form Error
❌ `<input type="text" aria-invalid="true">` (no feedback)  
✅ `<input type="text" aria-invalid="true" aria-describedby="error-msg">`  
`<span id="error-msg">Please enter a valid email</span>`